        <updateDate>2020-12-28T18:04:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safer Occupancy Furniture Flammability Act or the SOFFA Act</strong></p> <p>This bill adopts the California flammability standard as the federal standard for upholstered furniture. To meet the standard, the upholstered furniture must past a specific test of the materials' ability to resist smoldering when a heat source is applied.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
